              <div class="technique-description text-sm text-ctp-subtext1 leading-relaxed">Conciseness, Logic, Explicitness, Adaptability, Reflectiveness for robust prompt design</div>
              <span class="use-case inline-block bg-ctp-green bg-opacity-20 text-ctp-green px-2 py-1 rounded-xl text-xs mt-2 mr-2">Production AI</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="technique p-3 rounded-lg bg-ctp-mantle border border-ctp-surface0 cursor-pointer transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-ctp-blue hover:bg-opacity-10 hover:border-ctp-blue hover:translate-x-1" data-technique="cot">
              <div class="technique-name font-semibold text-ctp-blue mb-1">Chain of Thought (CoT)</div>
              <div class="technique-description text-sm text-ctp-subtext1 leading-relaxed">Step-by-step reasoning with "Let's think step by step"</div>
              <span class="use-case inline-block bg-ctp-green bg-opacity-20 text-ctp-green px-2 py-1 rounded-xl text-xs mt-2 mr-2">Math</span>
              <span class="use-case inline-block bg-ctp-green bg-opacity-20 text-ctp-green px-2 py-1 rounded-xl text-xs mt-2 mr-2">Logic</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="technique p-3 rounded-lg bg-ctp-mantle border border-ctp-surface0 cursor-pointer transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-ctp-blue hover:bg-opacity-10 hover:border-ctp-blue hover:translate-x-1" data-technique="tot">
              <div class="technique-name font-semibold text-ctp-blue mb-1">Tree of Thoughts (ToT)</div>
              <div class="technique-description text-sm text-ctp-subtext1 leading-relaxed">Hierarchical reasoning with exploration and backtracking</div>
              <span class="use-case inline-block bg-ctp-green bg-opacity-20 text-ctp-green px-2 py-1 rounded-xl text-xs mt-2 mr-2">Games</span>
              <span class="use-case inline-block bg-ctp-green bg-opacity-20 text-ctp-green px-2 py-1 rounded-xl text-xs mt-2 mr-2">Planning</span>
            </div>
            
            <div class="technique p-3 rounded-lg bg-ctp-mantle border border-ctp-surface0 cursor-pointer transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-ctp-blue hover:bg-opacity-10 hover:border-ctp-blue hover:translate-x-1" data-technique="got">
              <div class="technique-name font-semibold text-ctp-blue mb-1">Graph of Thoughts (GoT)</div>
              <div class="technique-description text-sm text-ctp-subtext1 leading-relaxed">Interconnected reasoning graphs with dependencies</div>
              <span class="use-case inline-block bg-ctp-green bg-opacity-20 text-ctp-green px-2 py-1 rounded-xl text-xs mt-2 mr-2">Architecture</span>
              <span class="use-case inline-block bg-ctp-green bg-opacity-20 text-ctp-green px-2 py-1 rounded-xl text-xs mt-2 mr-2">Complex Systems</span>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Learning Strategies -->
